title: GoPro: Tractor Drift
description:
Steeze meets agriculture when Filip Lindquist and the Vianor crew drop 225 horsepower into a 1956 Volvo BM Terrier tractor.

Shot 100% on the HERO3® camera

Morillo "Anabasis Odyssey"
